DashboardDefinitionComponents.Name: Week Attendance
DashboardDefinitionComponents.Parameters:
[{"WidgetSubTitle":"","WidgetType":"grid","WidgetFilterField":"","WidgetColor":"","WidgetHeight":400,"WidgetHeader":{"showTitle":true,"showSubTitle":false,"WidgetMetrics":{"visible":false,"Metrics":[]},"WidgetPeriodChooser":{"visible":false,"type":"","startDate":null,"endDate":null}},"WidgetDataSources":{"main":{"type":"querytext","value":"with EntryTime as (    
    select 
        ad.Attendance as Id,
        ad.[Time] as InTime,
        ad.AdjustedTime as InAdjusted
    from
        AttendanceDetail ad
    where 
        ad.[Type] = 0
),
ExitTime as (
    select 
        ad.Attendance as Id,
        ad.[Time] as OutTime,
        ad.AdjustedTime as OutAdjusted
    from
        AttendanceDetail ad
    where 
        ad.[Type] = 1
),
Timesheet as (
	select 
		v.UserId, 
		v.[Date],
		sum(v.ActualTime) as Actual
	from 
		Analytics.DatamartTimesheet v
	group by 
		v.UserId,
		v.[Date]
)
select 
	distinct du.Department as DepartmentName,
	du.UserTypologyGroup,
	du.HasImage,
	du.Oid,
	du.FullName as [Name],
	du.ExternalId,
    v.InTime,
    e.OutTime,
    v.InAdjusted,
    e.OutAdjusted,
	IsNull(t.Actual, 0) as Timesheet,
	a.TardinessTotalMinutes as Tardiness,
	sum(a.TardinessTotalMinutes) over (partition by du.Oid) as TotalTardiness,
	case
		when cast(v.InTime as date) = @FromDate then 'Monday'
		when cast(v.InTime as date) = @FromDate + 1 then 'Tuesday'
		when cast(v.InTime as date) = @FromDate + 2 then 'Wednesday'
		when cast(v.InTime as date) = @FromDate + 3 then 'Thursday'
		when cast(v.InTime as date) = @FromDate + 4 then 'Friday'
		when cast(v.InTime as date) = @FromDate + 5 then 'Saturday'
		when cast(v.InTime as date) = @FromDate + 6 then 'Sunday'
	end as WeekDay
from
    EntryTime v
        left outer join ExitTime e on v.Id = e.Id
        left outer join Attendance a on a.Oid = v.Id
		left outer join Analytics.DatamartUser du on du.Oid = a.[User]
		left outer join Timesheet t on (t.UserId = du.Oid and  cast(t.[Date] as date) = cast(v.InTime as date))
where 
	cast(v.InTime as date) = @FromDate or
	cast(v.InTime as date) = @FromDate + 1 or
	cast(v.InTime as date) = @FromDate + 2 or
	cast(v.InTime as date) = @FromDate + 3 or
	cast(v.InTime as date) = @FromDate + 4 or
	cast(v.InTime as date) = @FromDate + 5 or
	cast(v.InTime as date) = @FromDate + 6
group by 
	du.Department,
	du.UserTypologyGroup,
	du.HasImage,
	du.Oid,
	du.FullName,
	du.ExternalId,
	v.InTime,
    e.OutTime,
    v.InAdjusted,
    e.OutAdjusted,
	t.Actual,
	a.TardinessTotalMinutes","mapping":""}},"Filters":{},"QueryConfiguration":{"PreviousPeriod":{"Show":false,"KeyFieldName":"","Type":0},"RequiredFilters":["startDate","endDate"]}}]
